    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Athena example queries (billing export)\n\nReplace `${billing_database}` and `${billing_table}` with your Athena database/table.\n\nTop services by cost (last 30 days):\n\n```\nSELECT product_product_name AS service, SUM(line_item_unblended_cost) AS cost\nFROM ${billing_database}.${billing_table}\nWHERE from_iso8601_timestamp(line_item_usage_start_date) >= date_add('day', -30, current_date)\nGROUP BY product_product_name\nORDER BY cost DESC\nLIMIT 20;\n```\n\nCost by linked account and tag (example):\n```\nSELECT line_item_account_id AS account, COALESCE(tags['${tag_key}'], '<<none>>') AS tag_value, SUM(line_item_unblended_cost) AS cost\nFROM ${billing_database}.${billing_table}\nWHERE from_iso8601_timestamp(line_item_usage_start_date) >= date_add('day', -30, current_date)\nGROUP BY line_item_account_id, COALESCE(tags['${tag_key}'], '<<none>>')\nORDER BY cost DESC\nLIMIT 100;\n```\n\nNotes: Athena table schema depends on how the Cost & Usage Report is configured; `tags` may be a map column or separate columns (adjust query accordingly).",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.5.2",
      "title": "Athena Query Examples",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 19
      },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "content": "### AWS Cost Explorer CLI examples\n\nGet monthly cost by service for a date range:\n\n```\naws ce get-cost-and-usage --time-period Start=2026-06-01,End=2026-07-01 \\\n  --granularity MONTHLY --metrics UnblendedCost \\\n  --group-by Type=DIMENSION,Key=SERVICE\n```\n\nGet cost by tag (Key=Project):\n```\naws ce get-cost-and-usage --time-period Start=2026-06-01,End=2026-07-01 \\\n  --granularity MONTHLY --metrics UnblendedCost \\\n  --group-by Type=TAG,Key=Project\n```\n\nFor detailed historical exports, enable Cost & Usage Report to S3 and query with Athena as shown in the Athena examples.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.5.2",
      "title": "Cost Explorer Examples",
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
